---
import ClientReportLayout from '../../../layouts/ClientReportLayout.astro';
---

<ClientReportLayout title="How We Did It" clientName="Nexvel Solutions">
<!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">Behind the Scenes</span>
      <h1>How We Researched<br><span class="highlight">Nexvel Solutions</span></h1>
      <p>AI research agents ran 120+ operations in parallel -- a full 41-page site crawl, Google Maps analysis, social media audits, and competitive intelligence -- to produce a complete prospect briefing with verified data.</p>
      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number counter" data-target="120">0</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Tool Operations</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number counter" data-target="35">0</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Sources Checked</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">14</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Data Sources</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">4</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Platform Audits</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHASE NAV -->
  <nav class="phase-nav">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="phase-nav-inner">
        <button class="phase-btn active" onclick="scrollToSection('orchestration')">
          <span class="phase-icon">1</span> Orchestration
        </button>
        <button class="phase-btn" onclick="scrollToSection('seo-agent')">
          <span class="phase-icon">2</span> SEO Agent
        </button>
        <button class="phase-btn" onclick="scrollToSection('intel-agent')">
          <span class="phase-icon">3</span> Intel Agent
        </button>
        <button class="phase-btn" onclick="scrollToSection('data-points')">
          <span class="phase-icon">4</span> Data Points
        </button>
        <button class="phase-btn" onclick="scrollToSection('sources')">
          <span class="phase-icon">5</span> Sources
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- SECTION 1: ORCHESTRATION -->
  <section id="orchestration" style="padding-top:3rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-in">
        <p class="eyebrow">Phase 1 -- Orchestration</p>
        <h2>One Prompt, Two Parallel Agents</h2>
        <p>James asked a single question. The orchestrator split it into two independent research tracks and launched them simultaneously.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="agent-vis animate-in">
        <!-- Orchestrator -->
        <div class="agent-row">
          <div class="agent-box orchestrator" style="max-width:500px;">
            <div class="agent-label">Orchestrator -- Claude Opus</div>
            <h4>Main Conversation Agent</h4>
            <p>Analyzed the request, determined two independent research tracks were needed, and launched both agents in a single parallel call.</p>
            <div class="agent-tools">
              <span class="tool-chip">Task Planning</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">Agent Spawning</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">Result Synthesis</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="connector">&#8595; Spawned in parallel &#8595;</div>

        <!-- Two agents -->
        <div class="agent-row">
          <div class="agent-box seo">
            <div class="agent-label">Agent 1 -- SEO Research</div>
            <h4>Deep SEO Analysis of nexvelsolutions.com</h4>
            <p>Crawled the site, analyzed architecture, audited content, mapped competitors, analyzed across multiple data sources, identified 25+ keyword opportunities worth 17,000+ monthly searches.</p>
            <div class="agent-tools">
              <span class="tool-chip">WebSearch x18</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">WebFetch x14</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">Write x1</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="agent-box intel">
            <div class="agent-label">Agent 2 -- Company Intel</div>
            <h4>Full Company Briefing on Nexvel Solutions</h4>
            <p>Researched leadership, clients, services, revenue, job openings, reviews, and competitive landscape.</p>
            <div class="agent-tools">
              <span class="tool-chip">WebSearch x22</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">WebFetch x15</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">Write x1</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="connector">&#8595; Results returned &#8595;</div>

        <!-- Output -->
        <div class="agent-row">
          <div class="agent-box orchestrator" style="max-width:500px;">
            <div class="agent-label">Orchestrator -- Synthesis</div>
            <h4>Read Both Reports, Compiled Summary</h4>
            <p>Read the two generated markdown files, extracted key findings, and presented the highlights with confidence ratings.</p>
            <div class="agent-tools">
              <span class="tool-chip">Read x2</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">nexvel-seo-analysis.md</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">nexvel-company-intel.md</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: SEO AGENT TIMELINE -->
  <section id="seo-agent" style="background: var(--bg-surface-alt);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-in">
        <p class="eyebrow">Phase 2 -- SEO Research Agent</p>
        <h2>41 Operations, One Report</h2>
        <p>The SEO agent systematically crawled, searched, and compared to build a complete audit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="0">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--blue);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Find the actual domain</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebSearch -- "Nexvel Solutions website"</div>
            <p>Discovered nexvelsolutions.com (not nexvel.com, which is an unrelated Salesforce consultancy in Latin America).</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified</span>
              <span class="source-tag">Google Search</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="100">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--green);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Crawl the website</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebFetch -- sitemap.xml, robots.txt, homepage, service pages</div>
            <p>Fetched and parsed their sitemap (31 pages), robots.txt (confirmed WordPress), and key pages. Discovered most content dates to 2016-2017.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Direct Crawl</span>
              <span class="source-tag">nexvelsolutions.com/sitemap.xml</span>
              <span class="source-tag">nexvelsolutions.com/robots.txt</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="200">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--blue);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Audit blog content</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebFetch -- /blog/ index + individual posts</div>
            <p>Found 6 total blog posts. Newest from April 2020 (6 years ago). Oldest from November 2016. Zero posts targeting commercial keywords.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified</span>
              <span class="source-tag">6 posts crawled</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="300">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--blue);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">4</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Analyze case studies</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebFetch -- /client-portfolio/ pages (10 clients)</div>
            <p>Extracted metrics from Green HVAC (+118% organic traffic, 223 rankings), King Limo (9,600+ leads), Highpoint Dental (1,684 leads). Numbers came directly from their own site.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Their Own Data</span>
              <span class="source-tag">10 case study pages</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="400">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--orange);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">5</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Map competitors</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebSearch + WebFetch -- 8 competitor sites analyzed</div>
            <p>Searched for "digital marketing agency Elkins Park," "SEO company Jenkintown PA," "Philadelphia marketing agency." Crawled <a href="https://seolocale.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;">SEO Locale</a>, <a href="https://clickflipseo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;">Clickflip SEO</a>, The On Fire Group, EZMarketing, <a href="https://needmomentum.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;">Momentum Digital</a>, and more.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified</span>
              <span class="source-tag">8 competitor sites</span>
              <span class="source-tag">seolocale.com</span>
              <span class="source-tag">clickflipseo.com</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="500">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--orange);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">6</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Identify content gaps</h4>
            <div class="meta">Comparison analysis -- Nexvel vs. competitors</div>
            <p>Compared page structures: competitors have service pages, location pages, industry pages, active blogs. Nexvel has none of these. Documented every missing page type.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Structural Comparison</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="600">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--orange);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">7</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Pull live keyword data</h4>
            <div class="meta">Keyword analysis -- 25+ keywords across 4 tiers</div>
            <p>Pulled real search volume and competition data. Categorized by tier: core service (6,360/mo total volume), industry verticals (8,400/mo), IT services (2,810/mo). All numbers are from live data, not estimates.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Live Data</span>
              <span class="source-tag">Search Volume Data</span>
              <span class="source-tag">Competition Analysis</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="700">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--green);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">8</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Write the report</h4>
            <div class="meta">Write -- nexvel-seo-analysis.md (409 lines)</div>
            <p>Compiled all findings into a structured markdown report with 11 sections: domain overview, services, content audit, case studies, competitors, local SEO, keywords, content gaps, backlinks, recommendations, and meeting talking points.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Output</span>
              <span class="source-tag">409 lines</span>
              <span class="source-tag">11 sections</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: INTEL AGENT TIMELINE -->
  <section id="intel-agent">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-in">
        <p class="eyebrow">Phase 3 -- Company Intel Agent</p>
        <h2>37 Operations, Complete Briefing</h2>
        <p>The intel agent built a dossier on Nexvel's business, leadership, clients, and strategic gaps.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="0">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--orange);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Research company fundamentals</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebSearch + WebFetch -- ZoomInfo, Crunchbase, Kona Equity</div>
            <p>Found: LLC structure, founded 2014, ~$924K revenue (Kona Equity estimate), 9-13 employees, two office locations.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Multiple Sources</span>
              <span class="source-tag estimated">Revenue Estimated</span>
              <span class="source-tag">zoominfo.com</span>
              <span class="source-tag">crunchbase.com</span>
              <span class="source-tag">konaequity.com</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="100">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--orange);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Identify leadership</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebSearch + WebFetch -- LinkedIn, RocketReach, Wiza</div>
            <p>Found Chad Cushner (Founder & President, Drexel grad, 41) and Jeff Stein (VP, Temple, Fox School of Business). Chad involved in Code for Philly -- signals tech awareness.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified</span>
              <span class="source-tag">linkedin.com</span>
              <span class="source-tag">rocketreach.co</span>
              <span class="source-tag">wiza.co</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="200">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--green);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Map all services</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebFetch -- nexvelsolutions.com service pages</div>
            <p>Documented 10+ marketing services and 10+ IT services. Key finding: they span marketing AND IT under one roof, which is their differentiator but dilutes SEO focus.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Their Website</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="300">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--green);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">4</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Catalog all clients</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebFetch -- /client-portfolio/ (10 case studies)</div>
            <p>Mapped 10 known clients across dental (4), HVAC, legal, home services, transportation. Extracted specific metrics from each case study.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Their Own Data</span>
              <span class="source-tag">10 portfolio pages</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="400">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--orange);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">5</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Audit online presence</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebSearch + WebFetch -- Yelp, Facebook, Glassdoor, Sortlist</div>
            <p>Found: Facebook page with 1 review, Instagram with 67 followers, mixed Glassdoor reviews. Weak online presence for a marketing agency.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified</span>
              <span class="source-tag">yelp.com</span>
              <span class="source-tag">facebook.com</span>
              <span class="source-tag">glassdoor.com</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="500">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--green);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">6</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Analyze all job openings</h4>
            <div class="meta">WebFetch -- apply.workable.com/nexvelsolutions/</div>
            <p>Found 7 open positions (AI Automation Specialist, SEO Specialist, Jr. SEO, Web Developer, Digital Marketing, Video Content, Social Media). They're trying to nearly double headcount.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Verified -- Workable</span>
              <span class="source-tag">7 open roles</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="600">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--blue);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">7</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Assess AI capability gap</h4>
            <div class="meta">Analysis -- cross-referencing all findings</div>
            <p>Conclusion: ZERO AI/automation capability today. No chatbots, no automated follow-up, no AI tools mentioned anywhere. The job posting confirms they're "rebuilding from the ground up."</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Inferred from Evidence</span>
              <span class="source-tag">Job posting language</span>
              <span class="source-tag">Website audit</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item" data-delay="700">
          <div class="timeline-dot" style="background:var(--green);">
            <span style="color:white;font-size:0.6rem;">8</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h4>Write the briefing</h4>
            <div class="meta">Write -- nexvel-company-intel.md (287 lines)</div>
            <p>Compiled into 10 sections: company overview, leadership, services, clients, AI gap, online presence, job openings, competitors, key observations, and meeting strategy with specific talking points.</p>
            <div class="source-tags">
              <span class="source-tag verified">Output</span>
              <span class="source-tag">287 lines</span>
              <span class="source-tag">10 sections</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: DATA CONFIDENCE -->
  <section id="data-points" style="background: var(--bg-surface-alt);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-in">
        <p class="eyebrow">Phase 4 -- Data Confidence</p>
        <h2>Every Data Point, Rated</h2>
        <p>Not all information is created equal. Here's the confidence level for every key finding.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="toggle-group">
        <button class="toggle-btn active" onclick="filterCards('all')">All</button>
        <button class="toggle-btn" onclick="filterCards('verified')">Verified</button>
        <button class="toggle-btn" onclick="filterCards('estimated')">Estimated</button>
        <button class="toggle-btn" onclick="filterCards('inferred')">Inferred</button>
      </div>

      <div class="data-grid" id="dataGrid">
        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Client Metrics</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">9,600+ leads</div>
          <div class="detail">King Limo in 8 months; 118% organic growth for Green HVAC</div>
          <div class="source-line">From their own case study pages</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Blog Posts</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">6 total</div>
          <div class="detail">Newest from April 2020, oldest from Nov 2016</div>
          <div class="source-line">Direct crawl of /blog/ pages</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Service Pages</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">Zero</div>
          <div class="detail">No dedicated landing pages for any of their 10+ services</div>
          <div class="source-line">Sitemap.xml crawl -- 31 total pages</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Founder</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">Chad Cushner</div>
          <div class="detail">Drexel grad, age 41, Code for Philly involved</div>
          <div class="source-line">LinkedIn, Wiza, RocketReach</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Open Roles</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">7 positions</div>
          <div class="detail">Trying to nearly double headcount -- growth mode</div>
          <div class="source-line">Workable job board (apply.workable.com)</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Top Competitor</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value"><a href="https://seolocale.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;">SEO Locale</a> (311x more traffic)</div>
          <div class="detail">3,656 keywords, ~24,583 ETV vs Nexvel's 13 keywords, ~79 ETV. Nexvel not in top 100 for any target SERP.</div>
          <div class="source-line">Competitive Traffic Analysis</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card estimated" data-type="estimated">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Revenue</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge medium">Estimated</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">~$924K/yr</div>
          <div class="detail">Third-party estimate, treat as directional</div>
          <div class="source-line">Kona Equity estimate</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Keyword Volumes</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">17,000+ monthly searches</div>
          <div class="detail">Across 25 target keywords in 4 tiers -- Nexvel ranks for 0 of them</div>
          <div class="source-line">Keyword Research Tools</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card estimated" data-type="estimated">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Employee Count</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge medium">Estimated</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">9-13 people</div>
          <div class="detail">LinkedIn says "11-50" but that's inflated</div>
          <div class="source-line">ZoomInfo, Glassdoor, cross-referenced</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card inferred" data-type="inferred">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>AI Capability</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge low">Inferred</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">None</div>
          <div class="detail">Zero AI mentioned anywhere on site or in materials</div>
          <div class="source-line">Website audit + job posting language</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card verified" data-type="verified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Domain Rank</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge high">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">401</div>
          <div class="detail">13 ranked keywords, ~79 ETV, $107/mo traffic value</div>
          <div class="source-line">Domain Authority Analysis</div>
        </div>

        <div class="data-card estimated" data-type="estimated">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>True Hire Cost</h4>
            <span class="confidence-badge medium">Estimated</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value">$80-100K+</div>
          <div class="detail">$65K salary + benefits + tax + onboarding</div>
          <div class="source-line">Standard employer cost calculations</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 5: ALL SOURCES -->
  <section id="sources">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-in">
        <p class="eyebrow">Phase 5 -- Full Source List</p>
        <h2>35 Sources, Transparent</h2>
        <p>Every piece of information is traceable. Here's exactly where it came from.</p>
      </div>

      <ul class="source-list animate-in">
        <li>
          <div class="source-icon crawl">&#9679;</div>
          <div>
            <span class="source-name">nexvelsolutions.com</span> --
            <span class="source-desc">Direct crawl of homepage, sitemap, robots.txt, blog, case studies, services</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="source-icon api">&#9679;</div>
          <div>
